/AI_COLLABORATION.md                     @core-owner
/TASKS/                                  @core-owner

# @analyzer-owner: Analyzer & Taint
/analyzers/                              @analyzer-owner

# @agent-owner: Agent & Knowledge
/agents/                                 @agent-owner
/evidence/                               @agent-owner
/knowledge/                              @agent-owner

# @api-ui-owner: API, UI & Report
/api/                                    @api-ui-owner
/report/                                 @api-ui-owner
/ui/                                     @api-ui-owner

# 测试 - 按对应模块审查
